            <title><![CDATA[【别挤！#嘴角起疱可能是单纯疱疹#[二哈]】#嘴角起疱尽量别用手挤# 嘴角起疱，很可能是由1型单纯疱疹病毒感染引起的。单纯疱疹一般长在唇红缘、鼻孔周围、眼睛周...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【别挤！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%98%B4%E8%A7%92%E8%B5%B7%E7%96%B1%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%8D%95%E7%BA%AF%E7%96%B1%E7%96%B9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%98%B4%E8%A7%92%E8%B5%B7%E7%96%B1%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%8D%95%E7%BA%AF%E7%96%B1%E7%96%B9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#嘴角起疱可能是单纯疱疹#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%98%B4%E8%A7%92%E8%B5%B7%E7%96%B1%E5%B0%BD%E9%87%8F%E5%88%AB%E7%94%A8%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%A4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%98%B4%E8%A7%92%E8%B5%B7%E7%96%B1%E5%B0%BD%E9%87%8F%E5%88%AB%E7%94%A8%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%A4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#嘴角起疱尽量别用手挤#</span></a> 嘴角起疱，很可能是由1型单纯疱疹病毒感染引起的。单纯疱疹一般长在唇红缘、鼻孔周围、眼睛周围或耳垂等暴露位置。它的自然病程一般是7天，尽量不要用手去挤破它，否则容易加重病情👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6jHVI2S" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
